You know what God says?

17:36.569 --> 17:36.909
No, no, no.

17:37.530 --> 17:41.937
I will bless you on 90% far more than you'll ever experience with 100%.

17:42.258 --> 17:43.179
That didn't make sense.

17:43.479 --> 17:44.541
90%, 100%.

17:44.821 --> 17:48.467
But if you say so, I will tie as 10%.

17:48.487 --> 17:55.398
This just will be been doing with our life, going down the list financially, sexually, relationally, forgiveness, forgiveness.

17:55.418 --> 17:56.159
That didn't make sense.

17:56.520 --> 17:58.162
What makes sense is to hold a grudge.

17:58.562 --> 18:00.024
What makes sense is to be angry.

18:00.064 --> 18:04.049
What makes sense is to be bitter and to get back at people and seek revenge.

18:04.089 --> 18:06.011
That's what makes sense, Jesus' nod.

18:06.372 --> 18:07.173
Love your enemies.

18:07.273 --> 18:08.614
What?

18:08.634 --> 18:09.295
Where are you?

18:09.315 --> 18:10.977
