18:13.761 --> 18:18.867
But if you say so, I will do it.

18:20.108 --> 18:21.490
What if that was your mantra for life?

18:22.146 --> 18:24.468
It unleashes God's power in your life.

18:24.488 --> 18:25.309
That's the first reason.

18:25.429 --> 18:30.835
Second reason why obedience leads to an upgrade is because God is looking to give people his power.

18:32.256 --> 18:35.559
He's looking to give people his power, but he has to trust you.

18:35.659 --> 18:37.001
God wants to trust you.

18:38.742 --> 18:43.968
See, a lot of times our upgrade, many times our upgrade involves more influence, more authority, more impact.

18:44.148 --> 18:50.354
Like we want to erase at work, we want more, we want more money, but are we ready to handle more money?

18:51.330 --> 18:55.545
We would like a raise, we'd like a new position, but are we ready to have employees underneath us?

18:57.311 --> 19:00.162
We'd love to have a bigger family or get married.

19:00.262 --> 19:03.634
Are you ready to handle a spouse and a larger family?

19:04.802 --> 19:08.167
Like God wants to give us more, but does he trust us?

19:08.207 --> 19:09.870
He has to trust us to give us more.

19:09.890 --> 19:10.451
Do you agree with this?

19:10.491 --> 19:11.332
Yes or no?

19:11.352 --> 19:17.462
One for one time, Jesus said, if you're faithful in the small things, if you prove to be faithful and tiny things, I will give you more.

19:17.502 --> 19:19.906
But let's first work on the small issues.

19:20.046 --> 19:22.209
He wants to trust us with his power.

19:23.411 --> 19:24.413
But have we proven it?

19:24.813 --> 19:25.555
