You're the anxiety that you're struggling with, the anger issues that you have, whether it's issues of bitterness and resentment and you can't forgive, or whether it's financial struggles that you have, or your sexuality that you're confused about.

24:20.280 --> 24:33.313
If you can come to the point where you say, well, Jesus knows everything about everything, whatever he says about anxiety, whatever he says about sex, whatever he says about fear, whatever he says about anger, I'm just going to do it because he knows it.

24:33.493 --> 24:34.354
How many of you are there?

24:37.474 --> 24:38.215
A lot of hands went up.

24:41.980 --> 24:43.162
And why aren't you doing what he says?

24:45.264 --> 24:56.720
If you believe that, then why aren't you following through on how he says to handle those who are insulting you and hurting you and even harming you?

24:58.562 --> 25:01.786
Why aren't you following through on what he said in regards to sexuality?

25:02.287 --> 25:03.909
See, we've got to ask this question.

25:05.111 --> 25:07.474
Do we really believe that Jesus knows

25:07.618 --> 25:09.962
what's best about everything.

25:10.022 --> 25:16.932
Jesus's brother James wrote a book called James, and he wrote something in that book that I think is really good for us.

25:17.253 --> 25:19.796
He said, I want you to be doers of what my brother said.

