James says, no good.

25:37.122 --> 25:49.459
You actually have to do the sermon, not listen to the sermon, because if you just listen to the sermon and you don't do the sermon, you're deceiving yourself into thinking that you did something spiritual, okay?

25:49.480 --> 25:50.882
That's Jesus's brother James.

25:51.683 --> 25:55.748
The one who looks intently into the perfect law of liberty.

