Why does he call this book the law of liberty?

26:08.396 --> 26:16.685
Well, he got it from his brother, Jesus, who said, if you're my disciples, you're continuing my word and then you'll know the truth and the truth will set you free.

26:16.745 --> 26:17.927
That's where he got this.

26:18.347 --> 26:32.923
Like he's quoting his brother saying, if you want to be free from anxiety, if you want to be free from anger, if you want to be free from pornography, if you want to be free from stress, if you have to stay in the word and do what the word says, and then it will set you free.

26:34.165 --> 26:35.506
He calls it the law of freedom.

26:35.714 --> 26:38.939
and continues to do so, not being a forgetful here.

26:40.842 --> 26:42.505
What did Danny talk about this weekend?

26:42.525 --> 26:43.587
What did I read in the Bible?

