29:08.962 --> 29:18.436
Like, I'm a better father, I'm not a perfect father, I'm not a great father, but I'm a better father than I would ever be because Jesus told me, do not provoke your children to anger.

29:18.496 --> 29:23.323
Do not tease them, do not call them names, do not shame them.

29:23.524 --> 29:24.846
Now sometimes I do that.

29:25.306 --> 29:29.453
