29:41.054 --> 29:44.140
Jesus makes your life better, but he makes you better at life.

29:44.200 --> 29:53.258
There are so many times where all I wanted to do was hold a grudge against my wife because of something she said or something she did so many times.

29:54.139 --> 29:54.781
How could she?

29:54.841 --> 29:56.564
Doesn't she don't know?

29:57.766 --> 29:58.928
