30:05.265 --> 30:07.529
Is there any other idiots in the crowd?

30:07.549 --> 30:09.131
Like, this is stuff that goes through my head.

30:09.151 --> 30:10.974
Like, that's it, you know?

30:12.377 --> 30:16.644
And then Jesus comes on, hey, remember my command on forgiveness?

30:19.368 --> 30:19.688
Yeah.

30:21.592 --> 30:22.854
Forgive is the Lord forgave you.

30:22.894 --> 30:24.116
Danny, how much have I forgiven you?

30:24.797 --> 30:25.338
A whole lot.

30:26.580 --> 30:27.241
Go extend it.

30:28.903 --> 30:30.546
Give it out like I gave it to you, okay?

30:32.162 --> 30:34.525
Jesus makes your life better, he makes you better at life.

30:34.546 --> 30:35.267
