31:20.130 --> 31:31.645
Do you see it like it doesn't, it doesn't compute with, like if you're gonna call me Lord and you believe that I know everything about everything and that I will bless your life if you obey, why are you disobeying?

31:31.685 --> 31:32.947
Like I don't understand.

31:32.967 --> 31:34.909
