31:35.170 --> 31:36.291
He's not mad at you.

31:36.491 --> 31:37.593
He's not even mad at me.

31:37.613 --> 31:38.614
He's not mad at us.

31:38.995 --> 31:39.956
He doesn't wanna punish us.

31:40.216 --> 31:41.818
He's just going, he's like, what's going on?

31:43.520 --> 31:44.722
Like I've laid it out for you.

31:45.666 --> 31:51.232
with your finances and your sexuality and with your emotions and your fear and your worry and the anger and the bitterness and all these other things.

31:52.113 --> 31:53.334
Like, why won't you obey?

31:56.798 --> 31:58.680
I love God's heart through the prophet Isaiah.

31:59.982 --> 32:00.462
Listen to this.

32:02.244 --> 32:05.107
How I wish this is God's heart.

32:05.768 --> 32:08.431
How I wish that you would have obeyed my commandments.

32:09.072 --> 32:09.592
Do you feel it?

32:10.233 --> 32:11.194
I just love God's heart.

32:11.514 --> 32:12.435
Comes through the scriptures.

32:13.476 --> 32:14.898
How, it's like a dad.

32:15.362 --> 32:18.586
How I wish you would just follow what I said.

