33:22.156 --> 33:24.319
He's been trying to communicate to some of you, give up the alcohol.

33:24.679 --> 33:25.981
You know it's kicking your butt.

33:26.001 --> 33:27.182
You know it's going to ruin your family.

33:27.583 --> 33:29.325
You know it's going to hurt your health.

33:29.345 --> 33:30.186
You know you drink too much.

33:30.406 --> 33:31.508
He's saying, come on, let's go.

33:31.528 --> 33:32.068
It's time to stop.

33:32.249 --> 33:33.450
You know he said, give up the porn.

33:33.470 --> 33:35.212
Come on, can you be faithful sexually?

33:35.272 --> 33:35.533
Come on.

33:36.594 --> 33:37.155
Do what I say.

33:37.455 --> 33:39.117
Live a biblically sexual life.

33:39.197 --> 33:39.638
Come on.

33:39.658 --> 33:42.962
And you're like, nah, I'm just telling you.

33:43.106 --> 33:44.388
It's gonna hinder you.

33:44.428 --> 33:45.409
It's gonna hurt you.

33:45.789 --> 33:47.712
Where do you need to obey Jesus?

33:48.132 --> 33:49.514
Is it in the area of your finances?

33:49.554 --> 33:51.276
Like you fear what Jesus said.

33:51.296 --> 33:52.698
He said, given, it'll be given to you.

33:53.058 --> 33:55.060
Good measure, press down, shaking together, running over.

33:55.281 --> 34:00.207
I know he says to do that, but I know generosity is a thing for him, but I need to hold onto it.

34:00.247 --> 34:01.528
I need to hoard it myself.

34:01.608 --> 34:03.150
So I need all of it, 100%.

34:03.330 --> 34:04.212
Come on.

34:04.452 --> 34:10.699
I know that's what you feel and it's what you sense, but Jesus says something different.

34:12.001 --> 34:12.882
Forgiveness.

34:13.634 --> 34:16.138
giving, trusting.

34:17.461 --> 34:21.247
If we just simply do what he says, our life will be blessed.

34:23.371 --> 34:26.516
You know, the gospel is a simple message.

34:27.397 --> 34:30.723
Jesus said, repent and believe the gospel.

34:30.783 --> 34:31.364
What does that mean?

34:32.206 --> 34:35.010
Well, repentance is this concept of turning.

34:35.691 --> 34:39.538
It literally means to change directions or to change your mindset.

34:39.842 --> 34:40.943
to think a different way.

34:41.023 --> 34:47.290
So if we could look at Jesus' words when he started preaching his message, he's literally saying, change the way you think about life.

34:47.410 --> 34:48.672
Change the way you're doing life.

34:49.252 --> 34:53.777
You're doing life according to your own knowledge, your own wisdom, selfishly, egocentric, all that stuff.

34:54.298 --> 34:58.322
I want you to turn away from that, living in your own little kingdom, and I want you to step into my kingdom.

34:59.023 --> 35:00.905
In fact, he would say it like this, my kingdom is near.

35:01.225 --> 35:02.487
My kingdom is here.

35:03.428 --> 35:04.329
Step into it.

35:04.409 --> 35:07.312
Repent of that way and step into a new life.

35:08.573 --> 35:09.394
Life with God.

35:10.530 --> 35:14.276
You know that message is something that needs to be obeyed.

35:14.296 --> 35:19.824
A lot of preachers will say, believe and you'll go to heaven when you die.

35:21.066 --> 35:21.867
There's some truth to that.

35:22.988 --> 35:24.130
That's not what Jesus said though.

35:25.372 --> 35:31.501
He said, I want you to turn and enter in to a new way of life, a new way of living.

35:31.761 --> 35:32.743
Does that include believing?

35:32.883 --> 35:34.806
Absolutely includes believing.

35:35.086 --> 35:36.308
It also includes obeying.

35:36.829 --> 35:40.434
I'm turning my life around and I'm now gonna live with God.

35:40.802 --> 35:47.529
Jesus made that possible by dying on the cross for our sins, by removing the barriers so that we can step into fellowship with Him.

35:48.209 --> 35:49.451
Will you obey the gospel today?

35:50.832 --> 35:54.576
Will you turn today away from your kingdom into God's kingdom?

35:54.596 --> 35:59.921
Will you trust Christ that He died for you on the cross to forgive your sins and wash away all the guilt and shame?

36:00.822 --> 36:08.530
If that's you today, if you'd like to obey the gospel, if you'd like to trust in Jesus, I'm gonna say a simple prayer, take these words.

36:09.122 --> 36:11.385
and make them your own and step into life with God.

36:11.706 --> 36:12.968
Will you pray with me if you feel led to?

36:16.914 --> 36:28.251
Jesus, I turn today away from living my own way, my own life.

36:30.795 --> 36:31.757
And I turn towards you.

36:34.020 --> 36:35.122
I turn into your kingdom.

36:38.818 --> 36:45.887
Put my trust in my faith in you, in what you did for me on the cross.

36:48.069 --> 36:48.770
You gave your life.

36:50.873 --> 36:56.760
You died to pay for my son.

36:56.780 --> 36:59.803
And so I trust you right now.

36:59.823 --> 37:05.310
Wash me of my sin, cleanse me, and make me your child.

37:07.753 --> 37:08.594
And from this dayful,

37:11.170 --> 37:30.993
Teach me to obey so that your power, my influence, authority, and life will just get better as I follow your ways.

37:31.013 --> 37:32.054
I pray this in Jesus' name.

37:33.396 --> 37:34.997
Amen.

37:35.017 --> 37:37.380
If you just prayed that prayer, our church wants to celebrate with you.

37:37.420 --> 37:37.801
Amen.

37:38.141 --> 37:38.962
Amen.

37:41.378 --> 37:45.874
If you wouldn't mind, if you're watching online or whatever location you're at, if you wouldn't want, if you...

37:45.922 --> 37:51.207
mind, if you just prayed that prayer, could you text the word saved, S-A-V-E-D, to 65248?

37:51.767 --> 37:52.308
Here's why.

37:52.848 --> 37:56.531
We would love to get with you and support you in your new journey with Christ.

37:56.551 --> 38:01.095
We would also like to put a box in your hands, a saved box inside this box.

38:01.115 --> 38:09.963
There's a cup, there's a new believer's Bible in here with a reading plan to get you started on your new journey with Christ, a little bit about baptism, about how to get in a group.

38:09.983 --> 38:15.908
And so if you text the word saved to 65248, please grab one of these at your auditorium in the back of your auditorium.

38:15.888 --> 38:18.111
Can we give God glory one more time, guys?

38:18.191 --> 38:18.471
Amen?

38:22.816 --> 38:23.577
Will you pray with me?

38:23.937 --> 38:28.462
Father, thank you so much for the clarity of the Scriptures that you tell us to obey.

38:28.502 --> 38:39.815
Help us to be like Peter, who said, but if you say so, when we don't understand or when it doesn't make sense, and when it goes against what we're feeling and desiring, may we just trust you that you know best.

38:40.877 --> 38:45.522
Put our lives in your hands so that we can upgrade and experience abundant life.

38:45.762 --> 38:46.265
We love you.

38:46.507 --> 38:47.494
It's in Christ and we pray.

38:48.018 --> 38:48.279
Amen.

38:48.924 --> 38:49.427
God bless you.

38:49.447 --> 38:51.602
See you next week for week number four of upgrade.

